locality: Río Negro, 1.5 km East of Cerro de La Neblina Base Camp which is on Río Mawarinuma. 0 to 3 km South of main river. Elev. 140 m. 0º50'N, 66º10'W.
Departamento Río Negro, upper Río Baria. Lowland evergreen forest on hummocks along river. In clumps; only individual observed to be flowering among hundreds seen along the river.
